  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Six men nabbed for hoarding fuel",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Six suspects have been arrested for stockpiling fuel without licenses and selling it at high prices in several areas.",
        "Four suspects were arrested in Mawathagama, Paragahadeniya, Maswewa, We-Uda, and Welikumbura areas for illegally stockpiling fuel and selling it at exorbitant prices.",
        "Police said that 315L of diesel were seized from their possession.",
        "At the same time, Police arrested a suspect who was illegally stockpiling fuel in the Sandiveli area in Batticaloa and seized 550L of diesel and 258L of kerosene in his possession.",
        "Meanwhile, a suspect was arrested with 1100L of diesel in the Kotagala area in Dimbulapathana.",
        "The arrested suspects are due to be produced to the court on Monday (27).",
        "G7 aims to raise $600 billion to counter China\u2019s Belt and Road"
      ],
